race.comment: A good race. MELDUBIOUS (5) was an easy trial winner and was then heavily bet winning a CL1 comfortably over 1200m at Eagle Farm. Proven second-up and Rodd stays aboard. Strips fitter and he can take the next step. BARRELLING (7) races forward and missed the hat-trick by a whisker here in stronger. Has Maloney on today and will get all the favours from a handy barrier. He's a live chance. SOUTHERN CHARM (2) is up to this on her day and she raced favourite at Ipswich in stronger last time when finding a place. She will be around the mark. Ditto CHIEF IN CHARGE (3), who impressed winning a CL1 at Doomben. He will be hitting the line.
